{"tid":1127170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時諗以前啲人生活係點","createTime":"2019-04-27T01:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T04:06:52.000Z","uid":133611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7607fc2142c56aef8fb061852a2d94d93aefe399","tid":1127170,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"假設你冇紙筆喺身<br />\n講咩日子邊度等<br />\n感覺好容易聽錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫低佢 出錯你又唔知自己聽錯定對方講錯<br />\n無論咩嘢要confirm多一次都要打電話（因為你抄低嘅嘢可能係你抄錯<br />\n<br />\n而且「不見不散」呢個terms有啲恐怖<br />\n去錯地方日子等幾耐會走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等人嗰陣又on99冇嘢可以做<br />\n又冇方法知道對方去到邊<br />\n可能對方遲10-20分鐘已經好燥底<br />\n<br />\n古代嗰啲人係咪唔妥對方想殺咗佢都好容易？<br />\n冇證冇據 吹得我漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就想像到可能勁多冇人知道真相嘅奇怪事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行行下有咩事都冇得即刻報驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一輩成日話上一代資訊冇咁發達好啲<br />\n但我都唔太理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得好似好危險咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe5408c83fa68a841db14801a5a1f8e421fb61e","tid":1127170,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:58:29.000Z","msg":"都係咁過者 約好時間冇人準時咪踢住先<br />\n<br />\n好似返工咁 自動會到"},{"pid":"73647fd6a16d8646139588f299155ffdae27a4aa","tid":1127170,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"報官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我搵地方住都會搵附近有衙門嘅地方"},{"pid":"f9f400a19f286b6931f76469f752fcf7f2c01301","tid":1127170,"uid":228963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba95e4d04919dde795af62ce0aebea459325bbba","tid":1127170,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f400a19f286b6931f76469f752fcf7f2c01301","tid":1127170,"uid":228963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:04:27.000Z","msg":"應該有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要同屋企人飲茶食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8d74245380ee47824b41fc603d3e118af53b5e","tid":1127170,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73647fd6a16d8646139588f299155ffdae27a4aa","tid":1127170,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"報官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我搵地方住都會搵附近有衙門嘅地方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:04:45.000Z","msg":"去打鑼打鼓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2475f9f8ce8b6cb732391f9c4756f1ac4d6d389d","tid":1127170,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:22:42.000Z","msg":"古代有連坐<br />\n條村死左人唔拿拿臨捉條友出黎全村都同罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca32c26d898b1fd4063ab268b0a64858bbce0b9","tid":1127170,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:23:34.000Z","msg":"通常約係屋企等咗先"},{"pid":"1b5d2f28eb7fffcf77a8b5eab7856565f82315e9","tid":1127170,"uid":103333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"從前的日色變得慢<br />\n車馬郵件都慢<br />\n一生只夠愛一個人<br />\n從前的鎖也好看<br />\n鑰匙精美有樣子<br />\n你鎖了<br />\n人家就懂了<br />\n<br />\n記得早先少年時<br />\n大家誠誠懇懇<br />\n說一句<br />\n是一句"},{"pid":"b9ccf4df37516f9afae7ec223a02e0b091978b75","tid":1127170,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ca32c26d898b1fd4063ab268b0a64858bbce0b9","tid":1127170,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:23:34.000Z","msg":"通常約係屋企等咗先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁正"}]}